trans-unit.source: How to restore a database backup
trans-unit.target: Kako obnoviti bekap baze podataka

trans-unit.source: If you need to restore a database backup, we invite you to subscribe to a [1][2]technical support plan[/2][/1].
trans-unit.target: Ako treba da obnovite rezervnu kopiju baze podataka, pozivamo vas da se pretplatite na [1][2]technical support plan[/2][/1].

trans-unit.source: Our team will take care of restoring your database safely.
trans-unit.target: Naš tim će se postarati za obnavljanje baze podataka.

trans-unit.source: Why can't I restore it by myself?
trans-unit.target: Zašto ne mogu da je obnovim sam?

trans-unit.source: Your shop is hosted by PrestaShop. Although you can create backup files here below, there are core settings you cannot access for security reasons, like the database management. Thus, only our team can proceed to a restoration.
trans-unit.target: Vaš sajt hostuje PrestaShop. Iako sami možete kreirati kopiju baze podataka ovde ispod, postoje neke važne postavke kojima vi nemate pristup iz bezbednosnih razloga. Zbog toga samo naš tim može da izvrši obnovu baze podataka.

trans-unit.source: Disclaimer before creating a new backup

trans-unit.source: PrestaShop is not responsible for your database, its backups and/or recovery.
trans-unit.target: PrestaShop tim nije odgovoran za vašu bazu podataka, vašu rezervnu kopiju, obnavljanje baze podataka niti za vaše same podatke.

trans-unit.source: PrestaShop is open-source software. You are using it at your own risk under the license agreement.
trans-unit.target: PrestaShop je open-source softver, koristite ga na sopstveni rizik u skladu sa ugovorom o licenciranju.

trans-unit.source: You should back up your data on a regular basis (both files and database).
trans-unit.target: Trebalo bi sami da redovno pravite kopiju i fajlova i baze podataka.

trans-unit.source: This function only backs up your database, not your files.
trans-unit.target: Ova funkcija samo pravi rezervnu kopiju baze podataka, ne i fajlova.

trans-unit.source: By default, your existing database tables will be dropped during the backup recovery (see "Backup options" below).
trans-unit.target: Podrazumeva se da će postojeće tabele iz baze biti izbrisane prilikom vraćanja rezervne kopije (pogledajte opcije rezerve kopije).

trans-unit.source: Always verify the quality and integrity of your backup files!
trans-unit.target: Uvek proverite kvalitet i integritet fajlova rezervne kopije!

trans-unit.source: Always verify that your backup files are complete, up-to-date and valid, even if you had a success message appear during the backup process.
trans-unit.target: Uvek proverite da li su fajlovi rezervne kopije potpuni i validni. Ovo je preporučljivo čak i ako ste dobili poruku o uspešnom stvaranju rezervne kopije.

trans-unit.source: Always check your data.
trans-unit.target: Uvek proverite svoje podatke.

trans-unit.source: Never restore a backup on a live site.
trans-unit.target: Nikada ne obnavljajte rezervnu kopiju na sajt koji je u funkciji.
